CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 3, 1970, pg. 17 reads: "An Attractive Trio - Three of the attractive young ladies who modeled at the Harriet Tubman Guild's recent "Winter Fantasy," are shown above. Members of Letha Hunt's Mona Lisas are from left to right :Marian Henderson, Diane Franklin and Sondria Pettigrew. - Harris photos."Gloria Winston is Gloria Golden Grate's niece.
TitMainTitle: Gloria Winston wearing zippered mini dress, hat, and thigh high boots, standing in interior with triangular patterned carpet and ferns for Harriet Tubman Guild "Winter Fantasy" fashion show
